</li><li> In an episode of <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/TheSuiteLifeOfZackAndCody" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/TheSuiteLifeOfZackAndCody">The Suite Life of Zack and Cody</a></em>, Cody disguises himself as a girl when he enters a <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BeautyContest" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/BeautyContest">Beauty Contest</a> to win the prize money so he and Zack can buy bikes.
</li><li> In an episode of <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/ThirdRockFromTheSun" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/ThirdRockFromTheSun">3rd Rock from the Sun</a></em>, Sally decided she needed to experience a childhood, so she started acting like a little girl. This included styling Tommy's hair into pigtails and so forth. He did not enjoy it.
</li><li> In an episode of <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/WinginIt" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/WinginIt">Wingin It</a></em> Carl has to wear a dress and has to model it.
