</div><ul><li> In one of the episodes, the gang are <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PlayingHouse" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PlayingHouse">Playing House</a>. Kaeloo is the mother, Mr. Cat is the father, Stumpy is their son, and Quack Quack is forced by <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ControlFreak" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ControlFreak">Kaeloo</a> to dress as a girl to play the daughter.
</li></ul></li><li> <em><a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/TheLionKing1994" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/TheLionKing1994">The Lion King (1994)</a></em> has Timon and Pumbaa <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/WeNeedADistraction" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/WeNeedADistraction">providing a diversion</a>.
<div class="indent"> <strong>Simba:</strong> Come on, Timon. You guys need to create a diversion. <br><strong>Timon:</strong> What do you want me to do, <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TemptingFate" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TemptingFate">dress up in drag and do the hula?</a> <br><strong>*cue <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GilliganCut" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/GilliganCut">Gilligan Cut</a>*</strong>
