</li><li> <em> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/TheSimpsons" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/TheSimpsons">The Simpsons</a></em>: In the episode &#147;Two Dozen and One Greyhounds&#148;, Bart has his socks eaten by a group of Santa&#146;s Little Helper&#146;s puppies, necessitating him wearing Lisa&#146;s frilly pink socks (which is entirely due to <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RuleOfFunny" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/RuleOfFunny">Rule of Funny</a>, since her usual socks are white). He also has to wear a frilly pink skirt, even though his shorts are fine, apparently because he &#145;has to co-ordinate&#146;. He ends up being forced to go to school dressed like that.
