<ul><li> <a class="twikilink" href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/RobertPattinson" title="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/RobertPattinson">Robert Pattinson</a> used to be put in drag a lot by his older sisters. He grew out of it eventually.
